{"title_page": "P.C. Mittal Memorial Bus Terminus", "text_new": "{{db-spam|help=off}}\n{{short description|Bus terminal in North Bengal, India}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=May 2018}}\n{{Use Indian English|date=May 2018}}\n{{Infobox station\n| name             = P.C. Mittal Memorial Bus Terminus\n| native_name      = \n| native_name_lang = \n| symbol_location  = bus\n| type             = Private Bus Terminus\n| image            = PC Mittal bus terminus.png\n| alt              = \n| caption          = Front View of P.C. Mittal Memorial Bus Terminus<br>P.C. Mittal Memorial Bus Terminus, Siliguri\n| other_name       = Dooars Bus Stand\n| address          = Sevoke road, Siliguri\u2013734001 Dist: Darjeeling, [[West Bengal]]\n| country          = India\n| coordinates      = {{Coord|26.7419495| 88.4346380|type:railwaystation_region:IN|display=inline,title}}\n| elevation        = {{convert|120|m|ft}}\n| owned            = PCM Group of Industries\n| operator         = Siliguri Municipal Corporation\n| platforms        = 28\n| bus_operators    = [[NBSTC]] and Private operators\n| bus_routes       = 10present\n| connections      = [[North Bengal]], [[Bhutan]]\n| structure        = Standard\n| parking          = Available\n| bicycle          = Available\n| disabled         = \u267f Ok\n| code             = \n| zone             = Siliguri\n| website          = \n| opened           = 03/02/2001\n| closed           = <!-- {{End date|YYYY|MM|DD|df=y}} -->\n| passengers       = 5,000 per day\n| pass_year        = \n| pass_rank        = \n| map_type         = India West Bengal#India\n| map_caption      = Location in [[West Bengal]]##Location in India\n}}\n\nThe '''[[P.C. Mittal Memorial Bus Terminus]]''' is one the most important bus terminal in [[Siliguri]][[North Bengal]]. It is located on Sevoke Road, [[Siliguri]], [[Darjeeling district|District Darjeeling]]. It is from 5.4 [[Siliguri Junction railway station|Siliguri Junction]] railway station, about 8.2 kilometers from [[New Jalpaiguri Junction railway station|New Jalpaiguri Railway Station]]. Both State owned [[North Bengal State Transport Corporation|North Bengal State Transport Corporation (NBSTC)]] buses and private buses ply from here. The Terminus is named after the famous P.C. Mittal a social worker and a business man, who was a resident of the [[Darjeeling District]].\n\nP.C. Mittal Memorial Bus Terminus is Located at Sevoke Road in Siliguri. This bus Terminus was inaugurated by Honourable Chief Minister of West Bengal on the 3rd of February 2001. This bus terminus is maintained by Siliguri Municipal Corporation.This bus terminus handles more than 300 buses and bound for Dooars, Coochbehar, Bhutan and adjoining areas. The bus terminus has acted as a catalyst to a boom in construction activity in the whole area. Beneficiaries are nearly in about ten thousand commuters. Patients, School children, elders and the general public are benefited. People use this bus stand to reach hospitals, schools, Market, Divisional Courts, Banks and other connected institutions as this is situated in the heart of the town.\n\n== Amenities ==\n\n*\ud83c\udd7f\ufe0f Perking Available\n*\ud83d\udebb Washroom Available\n*\ud83d\udecb\ufe0f Restroom Available\n*\ud83c\udf71 Foodstall Available\n*\ud83d\udcd6 Bookstore Available\n*\ud83d\uddde\ufe0f Newspaper seller Available\n*\u2139\ufe0f Information center Available\n*\ud83d\ude8c 24\u00d77 Transit Available\n*\ud83d\ude95 [[Ola Cabs]], [[Uber]], [[Rapido taxi]] service available\n\n== Bus Routes ==\n\n*Siliguri-Jaigaon\n*Siliguri-Malbazar\n*Siliguri-Coach Bihar\n*Siliguri-Alipurduar\n*Siliguri-Phuentsholing\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n", "text_old": "{{db-spam|help=off}}\n{{short description|Bus terminal in North Bengal, India}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=May 2018}}\n{{Use Indian English|date=May 2018}}\n{{Infobox station\n| name             = P.C. Mittal Memorial Bus Terminus\n| native_name      = \n| native_name_lang = \n| symbol_location  = bus\n| type     