 Memorial Bus Terminus is Located at Sevoke Road in Siliguri. This bus Terminus was inaugurated by Honourable Chief Minister of West Bengal on the 3rd of February 2001. This bus terminus is maintained by Siliguri Municipal Corporation.This bus terminus handles more than 300 buses and bound for Dooars, Coochbehar, Bhutan and adjoining areas. The bus terminus has acted as a catalyst to a boom in construction activity in the whole area. Beneficiaries are nearly in about ten thousand commuters. Patients, School children, elders and the general public are benefited. People use this bus stand to reach hospitals, schools, Market, Divisional Courts, Banks and other connected institutions as this is situated in the heart of the town.\n\n== Amenities ==\n\n*\ud83c\udd7f\ufe0f Perking Available\n*\ud83d\udebb Washroom Available\n*\ud83d\udecb\ufe0f Restroom Available\n*\ud83c\udf71 Foodstall Available\n*\ud83d\udcd6 Bookstore Available\n*\ud83d\uddde\ufe0f Newspaper seller Available\n*\u2139\ufe0f Information center Available\n*\ud83d\ude8c 24\u00d77 Transit Available\n*\ud83d\ude95 [[Ola Cabs]], [[Uber]], [[Rapido taxi]] service available\n\n\n== Bus Routes ==\n\n*Siliguri-Jaigaon\n*Siliguri-Malbazar\n*Siliguri-Coach Bihar\n*Siliguri-Alipurduar\n*Siliguri-Phuentsholing\n", "name_user": "MB", "label": "safe", "comment": "Fix infobox image syntax", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/P.C._Mittal_Memorial_Bus_Terminus"}
